feat: move auto-backup from refs/heads/ to refs/guard/ (v2.1.0)

Migrates the auto-backup ref from refs/heads/cursor-guard/auto-backup
to refs/guard/auto-backup. This prevents accidental pushes via
`git push --all` (which only pushes refs/heads/*).

- Auto-migration: existing legacy ref is detected, moved, and deleted
- guard-doctor: detects legacy ref and suggests migration
- All docs updated: SKILL.md, recovery.md, README (EN+CN),
  config-reference (EN+CN), schema
- Short name `guard/auto-backup` still works in git commands
  (git log, git restore --source=, etc.)
- Delete via `git update-ref -d` instead of `git branch -D`
